items.title: Oil regulator cracks down on city gas firms; seeks uniform price of piped cooking gas
items.description: The government allocates natural gas priced at lower than market rates, called APM gas, to city gas retailers for sale to households as piped natural gas

items.title: Sona Comstar enters Chinese EV market, forms joint venture with Jinnaite Machinery
items.description: The Gurugram-based firm said it will invest $12 million, while its Chinese counterpart will put $8 million into the joint venture in the first phase

items.title: Passenger vehicles, two-wheelers fuel 22% growth in India's Q1 automobile exports
items.description: Across the segments, the total exports surged to 14,57,461 units in Q1, compared to 11,92,566 units in the same period of previous financial year
